Stainless Steel Gold Clover Necklace - Elegance Redefined

Elevate your jewelry collection with the exquisite Stainless Steel Gold Clover Necklace from Olor The Label.

Product Details:

Color: Gold

Design: Clovers

Material: Titanium Steel, Stainless Steel

Size: 45cm with Extension Chain for 50cm length

Key Features:

Waterproof: Crafted to withstand water exposure, offering worry-free wear.

Tarnish Resistant: Made from stainless steel, this necklace resists tarnishing, preserving its brilliance.

Stainless Steel: The necklace is meticulously created from durable stainless steel, blending elegance with enduring quality.

Care Instructions:

Keep the necklace gleaming by gently polishing with a soft, lint-free cloth, ensuring no scratches.

Store it in the provided boxes/pouches within a cool, dry area for optimal preservation.

Confidently Express Your Style: The Stainless Steel Gold Clover Necklace exemplifies Olor The Label's commitment to exceptional design and quality, allowing you to showcase your unique style with confidence.

Experience the allure of the Stainless Steel Gold Clover Necklace - a fusion of sophistication, longevity, and symbolic charm. Shop now and embrace timeless elegance.

In 2022, Olor The Label was established. Our goal is to design jewellery for every jewellery enthusiast and to upcycle real designer goods to make them more widely available and more affordable.

The word "olor" comes from the Cygnus Mute swan, a type of swan and a member of the Anatidae family of swans. It is indigenous to the far north of Africa and much of Europe. Swans represent grace, beauty, love, loyalty, and trust. Swan symbolism frequently refers to inner beauty and self-love. We want everyone to experience this when wearing Olor The Label.
